                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840421-69-defend804 t17840421-69-punish389"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
